text.tspan: This is such an important subject that Primus partnered with two
microbiological insttutes to test under real conditons the recontaminaton
The tests were made in a laundry using Primus barrier washers with a
physical separaton of the soiled and clean sides of the laundry rooms. The
establishments are certfed to be in conformity with RABC* by an external
The RABC is an abreviaton of Risk, Analysis, Biocontaminaton
and Control. RABC is a Quality Management System. The RABC
system is implemented to avoid microbiological contaminaton of
persons and products by laundry operaton and to provide defned
microbiological quality of laundered goods. The implemented
RABC-System is controlled by external experts on a yearly basis.
* NM: No Measurable / too many germs
** CFU - colony-forming unit is a measure of viable bacterial
The largest amount of germs are transmited by hand
Air is an important vector of propagaton of micro-organisms
Surfaces are a main vehicle of germ transmission too
